title: 이달의소녀탐구 #490 (LOONA TV #490)
summary:
0:01 -- JinSoul: "Why is my face so close?" She messes around with the zoom and zooms it further in to her face.
0:14 -- She looks around for people who are not busy and finds Kim Lip. Go Won: "You have been chosen~"
0:20 -- Lip shows her chocolate and she acts out a commercial.
0:34 -- She does some stuff that only makes sense to her as JinSoul and I are both confused and she exits.
0:43 -- OEC has their photoshoot and then Choerry asks why Lippie is acting so weird "Ms. Leader". JinSoul (while refferring to Kim Lip): "She has grown up!"
